<BR>
then you give the guy in the center of the tents 2 CYCLOPS skuls each wiegh 20 lbs. and then you need to go to a guy in the temple of Soulsek ro and get the couldran and put 6 items into it, So at this point I think the PALLY needs to be a master smith to complete ( only a thought )<BR>
those 6 items are as follows and forgive my spelling please:<BR>
Melatite       {no idea}<BR>
2 bars of ENCHANTED Platinum  {buy from vendor} then get enchanted<BR>
Mistmoor Granite    {Leering Gargole}<BR>
Sands of RO         {Sand Giant}<BR>
SOIL of Underfoot   {no idea}<BR>
