				Thanks for the info :-)<BR>
<BR>
So far from what I have been told and what others have completed is this:<BR>
<BR>
1 Melatite from the Gnomebot in Solesek eye, ( thank you very much, was in Steamfont and Ak'Anon for a long time looking)<BR>
2 &amp; 3  2 enchanted bars of Platinum ( easy just costly)<BR>
4. Soil of Underfoot ( from a quest in Kaladim you need to get 4 fairy dusts per Soil of Underfoot) note if you are a low level like me {level 15 Enchantress} go need Eurlisi sisters, 3 fairies spawn there or in GFay near Kelethin for fairies. the Fairy camp is way to hard for me.<BR>
5. Sands of Ro ( from Sand Giants )<BR>
6. Mistmoore Granite ( from a Gargoyle in Mistmoore, have hear of a named gargoyle and then just a leering, working to find out ASAP)<BR>
<BR>
You Combine these in the Cauldron from Lord Searfire and get Ronium ( you hope, this is the MASTER Blacksmith part)<BR>
then you go to a forge and COMBINE ONLY the MOLD and the BAR or Ronium ***** NO WATER *****<BR>
<BR>
IF any of this is wrong or incomplete PLEASE LET ME KNOW, this is as much as what I have been able to find from friends and sites and am almost done getting all the elements ( with TONS of help obviously )<BR>
